#. <section class="sutta" id="sn48.56"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn48.56:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.56:0.2"
msgid "6. Sūkarakhatavagga"
msgstr "6. The Boar’s Cave"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn48.56:0.3"
msgid "56. Patiṭṭhitasutta"
msgstr "56. Grounded"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.232"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.56:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ekadhamme patiṭṭhitassa, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pañcindriyāni bhāvitāni honti "
"subhāvitāni."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when a mendicant is grounded in one thing the five faculties "
"become developed, well developed."

msgctxt "sn48.56:1.2"
msgid "Katamasmiṃ ekadhamme?"
msgstr "What one thing?"

msgctxt "sn48.56:1.3"
msgid "Appamāde."
msgstr "Diligence."

msgctxt "sn48.56:1.4"
msgid "Katamo ca bhikkhave, appamādo?"
msgstr "And what is diligence?"

# At SN 22.48 the five khandha, including rupa are said to be sasava, which suggests that the term is similar to upadaniya, i.e. provocative of defilements.
msgctxt "sn48.56:1.5"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cittaṃ rakkhati āsavesu ca sāsavesu ca dhammesu."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant looks after their mind when it comes to defilements "
"and things that stimulate defilements."

msgctxt "sn48.56:1.6"
msgid ""
"Tassa cittaṃ rakkhato āsavesu ca sāsavesu ca dhammesu saddhindriyampi "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr "As they do so the faculties of faith,"

msgctxt "sn48.56:1.7"
msgid "Vīriyindriyampi bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr "energy,"

msgctxt "sn48.56:1.8"
msgid "Satindriyampi bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr "mindfulness,"

msgctxt "sn48.56:1.9"
msgid "Samādhindriyampi bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr "immersion,"

msgctxt "sn48.56:1.10"
msgid "Paññindriyampi bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr "and wisdom are developed to perfection."

msgctxt "sn48.56:1.11"
msgid ""
"Evampi kho, bhikkhave, ekadhamme patiṭṭhitassa bhikkhuno pañcindriyāni "
"bhāvitāni honti subhāvitānī”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how when a mendicant is grounded in one thing the five faculties "
"become developed, well developed.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.56:1.12"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
